"v. 举止(以一种特殊方式表现) 【英】 v. 举止，行为 (to behave or conduct in a specified manner) 【记】 com+port(带)→一个 人带有的全部仪态→ 举止 【同】 同根词：transportat ion(运输); portable(可携带的)派生词: comportment (n. 举止, 动作) 【例】 That little girl comported herself very well at the party last night. v. 举止; (与with连用)一致, 适合 【例】He comported himself as if he was the king 他的举动好像他是国王似的. 【记】com共同, port带－一个人带有的全部仪态－举止 【参】transportation(n 运输); portable(adj 可携带的)comportment(n 举止, 动作) 【记】port本身是个单词,除了门户之外,还有举止的意思，原指port携带东西的姿势； 【相关】deport 举止，驱逐，position 位置 comport (v.)  late 14c., from Old French comporter ""endure, admit, behave"" (13c.), from Latin comportare ""to bring together, collect,"" from com- ""together"" (see com-) + portare ""to carry"" (see port (n.1)). Meaning ""to agree with, suit"" (with with) is from 1580s. Related: Comported; comporting."
